00:13:18,079 --> 00:13:18,160
A2B1,

270
00:13:18,160 --> 00:13:18,180
A2B1,

271
00:13:18,180 --> 00:13:18,560
A2B2,

272
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,380
B2,

273
00:13:19,380 --> 00:13:23,760
and so forth. Nine components altogether,

274
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:28,140
nine independent components. Now, as it stands,

275
00:13:28,620 --> 00:13:32,120
this is not an anti-symmetric tensor. It's

276
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:35,620
