00:15:21,500 --> 00:15:25,000
A1, what do we have here?

312
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:30,000
A2B3 minus A3B2.

313
00:15:30,000 --> 00:15:36,440
And then, zero.

314
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:40,100
The diagonal elements are zero.

315
00:15:40,100 --> 00:15:42,440
There's off-diagonal elements here.

316
00:15:42,440 --> 00:15:44,900
And what about the elements below the diagonal?

317
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:47,000
The elements below the diagonal,

318
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,000
are, the same.

319
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:50,760
Same as the elements above the diagonal,

320
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,320
except opposite in sign.

321
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,640
So over here,

322
00:15:53,640 --> 00:15:58,540
