00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:43,760
C1 equals A2B3.

384
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:47,760
Minus A3B2.

385
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:50,760
And one, two, one, sorry, three,

386
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:53,760
the next one is two, of course.

387
00:18:53,760 --> 00:18:55,760
There's only one left.

388
00:18:55,760 --> 00:18:57,260
All right, and this is

389
00:18:57,260 --> 00:18:58,760
one, two, this will be A3,

390
00:18:58,760 --> 00:19:06,760
two, three, B1, minus two, three, A1B3, I think, right?

