00:19:41,760 --> 00:19:42,760
It's minus C2.

404
00:19:42,760 --> 00:19:44,760
It's minus C2.

405
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:48,760
So, in fact, what goes here is minus C2.

406
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:51,260
So the components of a vector

407
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:53,760
can always be displayed as an

408
00:19:53,760 --> 00:19:56,260
anti-symmetric tensor, or the

409
00:19:56,260 --> 00:19:58,760
anti-symmetric tensor can always be

