443
00:21:19,760 --> 00:21:23,760
as the transformation properties of a vector, and they do.

444
00:21:23,760 --> 00:21:24,760
They do.

445
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:26,760
So these are two different aspects,

446
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:28,760
or two different ways of thinking about

447
00:21:28,760 --> 00:21:31,760
the three components of a

448
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:34,760
vector in three, in three dimensions.

449
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:37,260
The cross product, and for many

